    "bug_report_description": "A white animal (appears to be a sheep or goat) is clipping through the wooden fence/railing at the top of the barn area. The animal's model is intersecting with a solid barrier that should prevent such movement. This collision detection issue breaks immersion and makes the game environment appear less realistic. The animal has a heart/love icon displayed above it, suggesting it's in an interaction state while experiencing this clipping issue.",
