    "bug_report_title": "Object Clipping Through Fruit in Character Interaction Scene",
    "bug_report_description": "A black shadow-like object or character hand is clipping through a red fruit (pomegranate/apple) in the cutscene. The black element appears to penetrate the fruit's texture in an unnatural way, creating a visual inconsistency. This breaks immersion and suggests improper collision detection between the character model and interactive objects. The fruit texture itself appears intact, but the intersection creates an unrealistic visual effect.",
